# Delta-chain test circuit
# Proves multi-level delta-cycle propagation
#
# A --> [NOT] --> B --> [NOT] --> C --> [AND(A,C)] --> OUT
#
# When A=1:
#   delta=1 : NOT fires -> B = 0
#   delta=2 : NOT fires -> C = 1
#   delta=3 : AND fires -> OUT = A & C = 1 & 1 = 1
#
# All at the same simulation time — proves delta chain settles correctly

signal A   0
signal B   1
signal C   0
signal OUT 0

not B   A
not C   B
and OUT A C
